item.title: Hamachi
item.dc:creator: @Fiendy Fiendy
item.description:
@Fiendy wrote:

Go to “my computer” or “Control Panel” Go to "add or remove programs’
Remove Hamachi then restart ur computer
go to their site and try to download it again…itll give u the installer on ur desktop. Install Hamachi and then restart ur computer if it asks u to…It should work then

BTW, I didnt say im gonna go back to hamachi yet…Im still trying to get the no-ip to work
